{
  "texts": [
    "In real-world scenarios, we have experienced various disturbances during video recording, which would significantly impact the accuracy of sign language recognition.",
    "For instance, there might be multiple persons in a video footage with different hand gestures.",
    "This would make the recognition pipeline hard to localise the signers.",
    "To address this, we will incorporate active signer detection into our pipeline.",
    "Then, our APP can correctly focus on the right signer.Moreover, since our sign recognition algorithm is trained on 2D videos in which signers perform Auslan in a frontal view, it might not accurately recognise signs when signers are not facing the camera."
  ]
}